        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_amal" xml:lang="os">
                <form type="lemma"><orth>amal </orth></form>
                <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>возможность</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>possibility</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>средство</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>mean</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <re>
                    <form type="lemma"><orth>amal kænyn</orth></form>
                    <sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>добывать</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>obtain</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                                <q>доставать</q>
                            </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                                <q>get</q>
                            </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                </re>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>k˳yd sæ banygænon, ūmæn nicy amal aryn</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>не нахожу способа, чтобы их похоронить</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>I find no way to bury them</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Нарт._сказ."
                            /><biblScope>13</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>æz, amal wævgæjæ, dæwæn nīcy baсawærdʒynæn</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>я, в пределах возможности, ничего для тебя не пожалею</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>I won't regret anything for you within the limits</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Брит."
                            /><biblScope>146</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>xūdinæg ū binonty ænæ færæz ænæ amalæj nywwaʒyn</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>стыдно оставлять семью без ресурсов, без средств</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>it is a shame to leave a family without resources, without funds</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Брит."
                            /><biblScope>139</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>Marine syvællony amaltæj xæssyn bajdydta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>Марине начала с трудностями растить ребенка</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>Marina started raising a child with difficulties</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Сека"/><biblScope>94</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>ci amalæj æj fesafon?</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>каким способом его погубить?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>how to destroy him?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MSt."
                            /><biblScope>8%l3%l</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>dæsnij amal in kænun ǵæwūj</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>надо раздобыть для него знахаря</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>one needs to get a healer for him</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Bes._Ka_ke"
                            /><biblScope>21</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>tillægi kust næ fiddæltæ tuxamælttæj kodtoncæ</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>хлебопашеством наши предки занимались с трудностями</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>our ancestors were engaged in arable farming with difficulties</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Sam."/><biblScope>130</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example>
                        <quote>ūd amælttæj airvæzt bīræǧ</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>едва-едва (с большими трудностями) спасся волк</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>the wolf barely (with great difficulty) escaped</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ЮОПам."/><biblScope>III
                            168</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>næ oʒænæn æz ænamal</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>я не буду без средств</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>I will not be without funds</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Iræf"/><biblScope>52</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>æz ba xuskʼæ sogtæ æma ciraǧi amal eskæmi fækkænon</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>я где-нибудь раздобуду сухие дрова и лучину</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>I'll get some dry wood and a splinter somewhere</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_MD"/><biblScope>1940 III
                            60</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang="ar" extralang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>ʽamal</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/>
                        <w>amel</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>действие</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>дело</q></gloss></mentioned>, а также ‘средство’, ‘хитрость’;
                    налично во всех кавказских языках, подвергшихся мусульманскому влиянию:
                        <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
                        <w>ʽamal</w>
                        <gloss><q>хитрость</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>дело</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>занятие</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="dar"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>нрав</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>нрав</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>характер</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ce"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/>
                        <w>oamal</w>
                        <gloss><q>нрав</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>обычай</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>возможность</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w>hamal</w>
                        <gloss><q>способ</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>средство</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>уловка</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>хитрость</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>кознь</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="abq"><lang/>
                        <w>amál</w>
                        <gloss><q>возможность</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>способ</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>выход (из затруднения)</q></gloss></mentioned>. Семантическое
                    развитие: от исходного значения ‘действие’, с одной стороны,—‘образ
                    действий’→‘поведение’, ‘нрав’ (), с другой — ‘способ действия’→‘прием’,
                    ‘уловка’, ‘средство’, ‘хитрость’ ().%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"
                            /><biblScope>93</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="ar" extralang="fa"><lang/>
                        <w>ʽamal</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><lang/>
                        <w>amel</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>action</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="trk"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>affair</q></gloss></mentioned>, and also ‘means’, ‘trickery’; it
                    is found in all Caucasian languages ​​affected by Muslim influence: <mentioned
                        xml:lang="lez"><lang/>
                        <w>ʽamal</w>
                        <gloss><q>trickery</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>affair</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>occupation</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="dar"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>temper</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>temper</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>character</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ce"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/>
                        <w>oamal</w>
                        <gloss><q>temper</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>custom</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>possibility</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w>hamal</w>
                        <gloss><q>way</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>means</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>trick</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>trickery</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="kbd"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>intrigue</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="abq"><lang/>
                        <w>amál</w>
                        <gloss><q>possibility</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned
                        xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/>
                        <w>amal</w>
                        <gloss><q>way</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><w/>
                        <gloss><q>solution (of a difficulty)</q></gloss></mentioned>. Semantic
                    development: from the initial meaning ‘action’, on the one hand, ‘a course of
                    action’ → ‘behavior’, ‘temper’ (), on the other — ‘mode of action’ → ‘movement’,
                    ‘trick’, ‘means’, ‘trickery’ ().%n<bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#ref_ОЯФ_I"
                            /><biblScope>93</biblScope></bibl>.</etym>
            </entry>
